gujarati.context:
Here are the translations:

A little written is considered a great deal, not kept by God's will on my head; 
Such a letter was written by Muktaanand, read and heard by wise Munivrnd.

Here is the translation:

This age has to be handled wisely; that one must think well in mind; 
Our situation does not have such a constraint, write what you say then it will be that way.
